channel.title: Damaged Insomnia
channel.description:
[center]Well, as most of you know I coded ScorpionScape, and Darkness Scape, both of which were "ok." Not even. Those two projects were a success, and for one final project I would like to do Damaged Insomnia. Well before I give any more information, I would like to explain the title of this project. For one, I'm tired of all these "Scape's," and "Isle's" I wanted an original name, therefore Damaged Insomnia. Ok now onto the information. I want this to be kind of like RuneScape, I'm also tired of private servers where you type ::money and you get the money, I want this to be some what of a challenge, when you level up it actually feels like an acheievement, and rares are rares,money is somewhat hard to make, where you actually have to earn it. All the commands that are currently in the server will be switched to admin only commands. For this project, I expect to put together a team, my first project for ScorpionScape didn't work out, surely the fact was because I was new here, with a post count of 5 asking to put together a team for coding. Before I show the application there will be only 1 job to apply for, Coder. The coder is also a tester, so I eliminated that we need 5 applications for different jobs that 1 person can do. What I mean by that is, if you coded it, you can test it. [/center]
[center]Here's the application form. [code] Name: Job: Why should you have that job: Experience:[/code][/center]
[center]One last note, if you get accepted I expect you to register on our forums, and be active, I want the same username you use on here on the forums for this Project, with a [i]DIFFERENT[/i] password. [/center]
[center]Now for our forums link - [url=http://damagedinsomnia.smfforfree3.com/index.php]Damaged Insomnia[/url][/center]
[center]╓╓╓Accepted for Coder╓╓╓ -Darkandlightjak5 -Dragonus18 -KiIIer -Legend Rene -i blkwolf i
╓╓╓Accepted for Forum Moderator╓╓╓ -llambo -OWNER 2007 -itzKyle
**Declined** tchandle[/center]
[center] Goals --------------------------- Incomplete Complete ---------------------------------- -New starting area -Specials -Almost Every Skill -Correct bonuses. RS like -99%mining -Barrows RuneScape like -PC - Optional -Client - Optional -Custom Pk zones -Half completed -Members -Actual KQ -Fight Pits -Anti SYIPKER[/center]
[center]Pictures[/center] [center]These pictures were of when I coded ScorpionScape. We will be using ScorpionScape as a base.[/center] [center][IMG]http://i123.photobucket.com/albums/o304/KyleTheAlien/monsters.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i123.photobucket.com/albums/o304/KyleTheAlien/Newstartingarea.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i123.photobucket.com/albums/o304/KyleTheAlien/jad.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i123.photobucket.com/albums/o304/KyleTheAlien/dungeon2.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i123.photobucket.com/albums/o304/KyleTheAlien/dungeon1.jpg[/img][/center]
